1
00:00:09,060 --> 00:00:11,500
=Episode 24=

2
00:00:23,440 --> 00:00:24,320
Young Lady.

3
00:00:24,490 --> 00:00:25,480
You're awake, Young Lady.

4
00:00:29,160 --> 00:00:29,960
Where...

5
00:00:30,399 --> 00:00:31,359
Where are we going?

6
00:00:31,359 --> 00:00:32,119
Back to Chizhou.

7
00:00:32,479 --> 00:00:34,119
Young Master He and Bao'er have left.

8
00:00:34,500 --> 00:00:35,359
Where's His Majesty?

9
00:00:35,960 --> 00:00:37,399
A coup may break out in the capital.

10
00:00:37,399 --> 00:00:39,400
His Majesty ordered us
to return to Chizhou first.

11
00:00:39,520 --> 00:00:40,679
If the situation stabilizes,

12
00:00:40,679 --> 00:00:41,880
he'll come fetch you.

13
00:00:42,039 --> 00:00:43,320
And if it doesn't,

14
00:00:43,320 --> 00:00:45,600
His Majesty said
you should find yourself a better man.

15
00:00:49,880 --> 00:00:51,679
Duke Zhen commands 200,000 soldiers.

16
00:00:52,210 --> 00:00:54,039
How could His Majesty
possibly withstand that?

17
00:01:12,120 --> 00:01:14,159
(Why has the prayer bread
turned red?)

18
00:01:20,159 --> 00:01:21,319
This isn't a prayer bead.

19
00:01:21,640 --> 00:01:22,480
What is this?

20
00:01:26,920 --> 00:01:27,760
Medicine.

21
00:01:29,359 --> 00:01:31,719
The blood must've triggered
the medicinal properties.

22
00:01:33,760 --> 00:01:34,480
Could it be...

23
00:01:36,040 --> 00:01:37,319
I only remember

24
00:01:37,320 --> 00:01:39,780
my mother often went to Mount Nanhua
with someone to collect herbs.

25
00:01:40,359 --> 00:01:42,319
This is a portrait of my mother
and Madam Lian.

26
00:01:47,920 --> 00:01:48,840
I understand now.

27
00:01:49,760 --> 00:01:52,680
This is what my mother protected
with her life

28
00:01:53,280 --> 00:01:54,959
after countless trips to Mount Nanhua.

29
00:01:55,519 --> 00:01:56,400
What is it?

30
00:02:02,159 --> 00:02:03,159
The antidote.

31
00:02:05,040 --> 00:02:05,920
Yiqing once said

32
00:02:06,280 --> 00:02:07,359
my mother's prayer beads

33
00:02:07,359 --> 00:02:08,800
only had 108 beads.

34
00:02:09,439 --> 00:02:11,000
Before she died,

35
00:02:11,280 --> 00:02:13,159
she deliberately added one more.

36
00:02:15,039 --> 00:02:15,879
So

37
00:02:17,560 --> 00:02:19,479
my mother hid the antidote here

38
00:02:19,479 --> 00:02:20,319
all along.

39
00:02:21,759 --> 00:02:22,280
Handan.

40
00:02:22,520 --> 00:02:22,879
Quick.

41
00:02:22,919 --> 00:02:23,730
We're returning to the capital.

42
00:02:24,759 --> 00:02:26,879
But the Duke Zhen Army
has besieged the city.

43
00:02:26,879 --> 00:02:28,639
We can't get close to His Majesty.

44
00:02:28,960 --> 00:02:31,719
Why don't we follow His Majesty's orders
and return to Chizhou first?

45
00:02:31,719 --> 00:02:33,080
His Majesty can't be harmed.

46
00:02:33,639 --> 00:02:35,439
Manshu Tears will kill him.

47
00:02:36,199 --> 00:02:37,759
For the sake of the realm, if he dies,

48
00:02:37,760 --> 00:02:38,990
the realm will fall into chaos.

49
00:02:39,039 --> 00:02:40,990
Neither you nor I
will have anywhere left to survive.

50
00:02:41,039 --> 00:02:41,960
And personally,

51
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:43,719
I can't let him die either.

52
00:02:44,120 --> 00:02:44,639
Hurry.

53
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:45,560
Who are you?

54
00:02:58,680 --> 00:02:59,759
Jiang Chen?

55
00:03:00,060 --> 00:03:02,940
(Jiang Residence)

56
00:03:03,300 --> 00:03:04,250
I prepared fish congee.

57
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:05,919
Eat it while it's hot.

58
00:03:06,960 --> 00:03:08,240
Is His Majesty safe?

59
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:12,140
His Majesty fought his way
to the throne through bloodshed.

60
00:03:12,159 --> 00:03:13,560
He endured countless hardships.

61
00:03:14,319 --> 00:03:15,599
Even so,

62
00:03:16,199 --> 00:03:17,800
does he mean he deserves to be used

63
00:03:18,039 --> 00:03:19,000
and deceived by you?

64
00:03:20,319 --> 00:03:22,159
I don't understand what you mean.

65
00:03:22,759 --> 00:03:23,919
He treated you as a friend.

66
00:03:24,479 --> 00:03:26,159
No matter what your father did to him,

67
00:03:26,680 --> 00:03:28,120
he never once doubted you.

68
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:30,639
He even tried to shield you from it all

69
00:03:30,670 --> 00:03:32,800
and let you remain
a clean and honorable young master.

70
00:03:35,080 --> 00:03:36,439
You don't deserve to be his friend.

71
00:03:37,280 --> 00:03:38,599
Shut up, Shen Zhinian.

72
00:03:39,210 --> 00:03:41,360
You've been trying to get close to me
this whole time.

73
00:03:43,080 --> 00:03:43,680
I suppose

74
00:03:44,479 --> 00:03:45,719
it was because you hated him.

75
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:48,000
You wanted

76
00:03:49,159 --> 00:03:50,159
whatever he valued.

77
00:03:54,080 --> 00:03:56,199
Weiqi is a game
of strategy and patience.

78
00:03:57,919 --> 00:03:58,919
This time,

79
00:03:59,639 --> 00:04:00,360
I'll win.

80
00:04:09,159 --> 00:04:10,560
Do you think His Majesty will guess

81
00:04:10,610 --> 00:04:12,580
that the real military tally
of the Duke Zhen Army

82
00:04:12,599 --> 00:04:13,439
is with you?

83
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:14,599
It doesn't matter.

84
00:04:15,879 --> 00:04:16,680
Without the antidote,

85
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:17,519
he's as good as dead.

86
00:04:18,240 --> 00:04:19,120
Sooner or later,

87
00:04:19,130 --> 00:04:20,590
someone else will sit on that throne.

88
00:04:41,560 --> 00:04:43,160
Little White Snake?

89
00:04:43,480 --> 00:04:45,079
Why are you here?

90
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:05,600
How did you get here?

91
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:06,800
You're not hurt, are you?

92
00:05:07,959 --> 00:05:08,759
I'm fine.

93
00:05:09,520 --> 00:05:11,330
I noticed Little White Snake
acting restless,

94
00:05:11,340 --> 00:05:12,890
so I guessed something must've happened.

95
00:05:19,079 --> 00:05:20,000
Eat this.

96
00:05:20,680 --> 00:05:21,600
What is it?

97
00:05:22,439 --> 00:05:23,480
You're quite trusting.

98
00:05:24,020 --> 00:05:25,490
Aren't you afraid I might poison you?

99
00:05:26,360 --> 00:05:27,199
You wouldn't.

100
00:05:30,879 --> 00:05:31,759
Well.

101
00:05:32,360 --> 00:05:34,240
How do you feel now?

102
00:05:36,920 --> 00:05:38,439
The burning in my chest

103
00:05:39,439 --> 00:05:40,680
is fading.

104
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:44,879
My guess is right.

105
00:05:45,439 --> 00:05:46,680
What exactly happened?

106
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:50,639
The person my mother met

107
00:05:51,439 --> 00:05:53,079
was His Majesty's loyal servant,

108
00:05:53,439 --> 00:05:54,040
Madam Lian.

109
00:05:55,839 --> 00:05:56,680
My mother

110
00:05:56,839 --> 00:05:58,240
once gathered herbs at Mount Nanhua,

111
00:05:59,199 --> 00:06:01,879
but the medicine was never used
on the people around her.

112
00:06:02,519 --> 00:06:03,639
So I guessed

113
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:05,879
she gave it to Madam Lian instead.

114
00:06:07,700 --> 00:06:09,360
And the Peng fish
in the imperial temple.

115
00:06:11,360 --> 00:06:12,720
It came from your mother too?

116
00:06:16,120 --> 00:06:18,319
My mother and Madam Lian
came from the same hometown.

117
00:06:18,639 --> 00:06:20,759
She knew your situation was dangerous

118
00:06:20,900 --> 00:06:22,240
and feared the antidote
would be discovered

119
00:06:22,240 --> 00:06:23,120
and destroyed,

120
00:06:23,879 --> 00:06:24,839
so she hid it

121
00:06:25,279 --> 00:06:26,360
inside the prayer beads.

122
00:06:29,399 --> 00:06:30,600
I see.

123
00:06:36,460 --> 00:06:37,680
We should leave this place now.

124
00:06:38,240 --> 00:06:38,959
Also,

125
00:06:39,439 --> 00:06:41,240
Jiang Chen locked Handan away
somewhere else.

126
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:43,279
Don't worry.

127
00:06:43,920 --> 00:06:44,759
She'll be alright.

128
00:06:45,079 --> 00:06:45,399
Mm.

129
00:06:55,879 --> 00:06:57,519
Your Majesty, why come so late at night

130
00:06:57,519 --> 00:06:58,720
without notice?

131
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:00,550
I could've prepared to greet you sooner.

132
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:02,519
Stop now,

133
00:07:02,759 --> 00:07:03,480
Jiang Chen.

134
00:07:03,720 --> 00:07:04,920
I've never made a move.

135
00:07:05,319 --> 00:07:06,680
What is there for me to stop?

136
00:07:07,199 --> 00:07:08,360
What I don't understand is

137
00:07:08,920 --> 00:07:10,639
that you clearly went after Prince Song,

138
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:12,319
why did you turn back halfway?

139
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:14,680
Because I never intended
to go after him.

140
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:15,759
Why?

141
00:07:17,010 --> 00:07:19,500
You shouldn't have let Shen Nanqiao
leave behind that prophecy,

142
00:07:19,920 --> 00:07:21,319
saying I would kill you.

143
00:07:21,839 --> 00:07:22,839
Just because of that?

144
00:07:23,519 --> 00:07:25,399
Surely you didn't think

145
00:07:25,690 --> 00:07:27,519
Shen Zhinian would turn against me
over it?

146
00:07:28,839 --> 00:07:30,319
She praised you as a noble gentleman.

147
00:07:30,690 --> 00:07:31,720
You actually believed her?

148
00:07:32,519 --> 00:07:33,439
You don't know her.

149
00:07:34,360 --> 00:07:35,399
She's smooth-tongued.

150
00:07:36,399 --> 00:07:37,920
Even when she hated me the most,

151
00:07:38,260 --> 00:07:40,370
she still praised me
as if I were the moon in the heavens.

152
00:07:41,199 --> 00:07:42,000
Enough!

153
00:07:42,920 --> 00:07:44,279
The moon in the heavens?

154
00:07:44,700 --> 00:07:46,890
You're nothing but filth
that crawled out of a kennel.

155
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:49,360
Your tongue can be just as vicious.

156
00:07:52,800 --> 00:07:54,020
Since things have come to this,

157
00:07:54,399 --> 00:07:55,879
there's no need to pretend anymore.

158
00:07:57,839 --> 00:07:59,439
Shen Zhinian was right.

159
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:02,079
I hate you.

160
00:08:03,279 --> 00:08:04,959
My father could've
become emperor himself,

161
00:08:05,319 --> 00:08:06,600
but he brought you back

162
00:08:06,620 --> 00:08:08,079
and made me serve you
as my master.

163
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:11,879
If you wanted the throne,

164
00:08:13,290 --> 00:08:14,439
I could've handed it to you.

165
00:08:15,420 --> 00:08:16,990
But since you insist on
taking it by force,

166
00:08:17,660 --> 00:08:18,720
I refuse to give it to you.

167
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:20,040
You leave me no choice.

168
00:08:20,560 --> 00:08:21,800
For old times' sake,

169
00:08:22,839 --> 00:08:24,000
I'll leave your body intact.

170
00:08:25,279 --> 00:08:25,879
Step back.

171
00:08:26,060 --> 00:08:27,120
Can you handle this alone?

172
00:08:27,319 --> 00:08:28,680
Who said I came alone?

173
00:08:32,799 --> 00:08:33,759
Jiang Chen,

174
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:35,519
considering our past acquaintance,

175
00:08:36,879 --> 00:08:38,360
I'll leave your body intact.

176
00:08:57,960 --> 00:08:58,759
Jiang Chen,

177
00:08:59,159 --> 00:08:59,960
stop this.

178
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:02,400
The Duke Zhen Army
mustn't enter the capital.

179
00:09:02,410 --> 00:09:03,740
You have no military achievements.

180
00:09:03,759 --> 00:09:05,090
You won't be able to control them.

181
00:09:05,480 --> 00:09:06,679
I'm the Duke's son.

182
00:09:06,679 --> 00:09:07,700
I hold the military tally.

183
00:09:07,759 --> 00:09:09,159
Of course they'll obey me.

184
00:09:09,160 --> 00:09:10,900
You've walked this path with me
all these years.

185
00:09:10,919 --> 00:09:12,990
You should know better than anyone
what kind of people they are.

186
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:15,120
Your father has indulged their greed
for far too long.

187
00:09:15,720 --> 00:09:16,840
Once they get the chance,

188
00:09:16,840 --> 00:09:18,240
they'll tear each other apart.

189
00:09:18,919 --> 00:09:19,960
The people of Daliang

190
00:09:20,240 --> 00:09:21,440
don't deserve such suffering.

191
00:09:21,679 --> 00:09:23,440
Stop being sanctimonious.

192
00:09:23,620 --> 00:09:25,799
You know perfectly well
how many lives you've taken.

193
00:09:26,039 --> 00:09:27,600
I only kill those who deserve it.

194
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:28,799
Enough talk.

195
00:09:29,279 --> 00:09:31,279
I've spent ten years pretending
in front of you.

196
00:09:32,039 --> 00:09:33,000
I'm sick of it.

197
00:09:33,350 --> 00:09:35,190
Today, you and I settle this
once and for all.

198
00:09:45,919 --> 00:09:46,900
Let go of Young Master,

199
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:47,519
or

200
00:09:47,720 --> 00:09:48,879
I'll kill Shen Zhinian.

201
00:10:07,679 --> 00:10:08,720
Luo Hao!

202
00:10:11,840 --> 00:10:12,679
Jiang Chen,

203
00:10:13,679 --> 00:10:15,240
since I entered the Duke Residence,

204
00:10:16,279 --> 00:10:18,000
whether in study or martial arts,

205
00:10:18,400 --> 00:10:19,799
I've always held back for your sake.

206
00:10:20,919 --> 00:10:21,799
What did you say?

207
00:10:24,240 --> 00:10:26,000
You couldn't surpass me,

208
00:10:26,080 --> 00:10:28,000
so Duke Zhen forced you
to kill your own mentor.

209
00:10:32,480 --> 00:10:33,480
Why are you trembling?

210
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:35,000
Stab him.

211
00:10:41,039 --> 00:10:42,120
From that day on,

212
00:10:42,799 --> 00:10:44,360
I yielded to you in everything.

213
00:10:45,480 --> 00:10:46,399
You're lying!

214
00:10:51,039 --> 00:10:52,120
Leave.

215
00:10:53,960 --> 00:10:55,000
I don't want to kill you.

216
00:10:59,639 --> 00:11:00,600
Nangong Xuanyu!

217
00:11:13,080 --> 00:11:15,840
I don't need your pity.

218
00:11:46,039 --> 00:11:46,559
Your Majesty,

219
00:11:47,100 --> 00:11:49,200
Duke Zhen Army has sent assassins
into the palace.

220
00:11:57,039 --> 00:11:57,960
Stay here.

221
00:11:58,000 --> 00:11:58,990
This is the safest place.

222
00:11:59,200 --> 00:12:00,759
Duke Zhen commands 200,000 soldiers.

223
00:12:00,800 --> 00:12:01,990
Are you confident you can win?

224
00:12:02,600 --> 00:12:03,679
With this position

225
00:12:03,919 --> 00:12:04,960
comes responsibilities.

226
00:12:05,330 --> 00:12:07,720
I don't want to see fathers and sons
turn against each other,

227
00:12:08,039 --> 00:12:09,660
or mothers separated from their children
ever again.

228
00:12:09,879 --> 00:12:10,519
Mm.

229
00:12:10,679 --> 00:12:11,519
You'll win.

230
00:12:11,919 --> 00:12:12,679
I'll wait for you.

231
00:12:26,679 --> 00:12:28,440
(In the first year
of Emperor Xuan's reign,)

232
00:12:28,559 --> 00:12:31,519
(news of Duke Zhen's death
spread through the army.)

233
00:12:31,799 --> 00:12:35,159
(The Duke Zhen Army launched an assault
straight toward the palace.)

234
00:12:35,440 --> 00:12:37,720
(Emperor Xuan remained calm
in the face of danger.)

235
00:12:37,840 --> 00:12:41,120
(He deployed 200,000 Scarlet Phoenix Army
left behind by his maternal family)

236
00:12:41,200 --> 00:12:42,799
(and personally led the battle.)

237
00:12:43,399 --> 00:12:45,240
(The war reached a stalemate,)

238
00:12:45,480 --> 00:12:48,240
(and blood stained the palace.)

239
00:12:53,679 --> 00:12:55,080
Do you think he won?

240
00:12:55,639 --> 00:12:57,600
It's been two days.
Why is there still no news?

241
00:12:58,559 --> 00:13:00,279
You should've gone with him.

242
00:13:00,600 --> 00:13:02,960
At least you could've bitten
a few enemies to death for him.

243
00:13:05,879 --> 00:13:06,840
No.

244
00:13:07,559 --> 00:13:08,879
I need to go see for myself.

245
00:13:12,159 --> 00:13:13,480
Zhinian.

246
00:13:13,480 --> 00:13:19,300
♪Falling at first sight,
a life of turmoil wasted♪

247
00:13:20,100 --> 00:13:26,500
♪Dim lamps, concerns unheard by anyone♪

248
00:13:26,940 --> 00:13:32,820
♪All the spring colors
lean toward one person♪

249
00:13:34,260 --> 00:13:37,900
♪Faint rouge hides
the tenderness in the eyes♪

250
00:13:37,900 --> 00:13:41,180
♪Every step is treacherous,
regardless of the world♪

251
00:13:41,180 --> 00:13:45,060
♪Flowers wither easily,
but obsession remains♪

252
00:13:45,060 --> 00:13:48,660
♪The world is gentle
only because of you♪

253
00:14:01,140 --> 00:14:03,740
(Tinglan Palace)

254
00:14:07,720 --> 00:14:09,759
Lady Shen, we've found your grandfather.

255
00:14:10,240 --> 00:14:10,840
Grandfather!

256
00:14:11,000 --> 00:14:11,720
Zhinian.

257
00:14:12,860 --> 00:14:13,559
Are you alright?

258
00:14:13,639 --> 00:14:14,399
I'm fine.

259
00:14:14,840 --> 00:14:15,200
Come.

260
00:14:15,200 --> 00:14:15,960
Sit.

261
00:14:18,500 --> 00:14:19,890
Your grandfather is quite capable.

262
00:14:20,000 --> 00:14:21,990
After escaping into the mountains,
he hid himself away.

263
00:14:22,000 --> 00:14:23,720
Both the Empress's men
and His Majesty's guards

264
00:14:23,720 --> 00:14:24,710
searched the mountains seven times,

265
00:14:24,720 --> 00:14:25,830
and they couldn't find him.

266
00:14:30,399 --> 00:14:32,360
Grandfather, you must've suffered a lot.

267
00:14:33,639 --> 00:14:35,240
Young Lady, we've found her.

268
00:14:35,240 --> 00:14:37,090
She was locked in the Jiang family's
dungeon the whole time.

269
00:14:37,440 --> 00:14:38,000
Mm.

270
00:14:38,960 --> 00:14:39,639
Wen Ling,

271
00:14:39,919 --> 00:14:41,679
please take my grandfather to rest.

272
00:14:41,840 --> 00:14:42,399
Yes.

273
00:14:42,720 --> 00:14:44,159
Grandfather, go get some rest.

274
00:14:44,480 --> 00:14:45,679
I'll invite you over again

275
00:14:45,790 --> 00:14:46,759
when it's time to eat.

276
00:14:46,759 --> 00:14:47,519
Alright.

277
00:14:48,120 --> 00:14:48,720
Please.

278
00:15:11,399 --> 00:15:13,759
Your parents have returned to Chizhou.

279
00:15:14,090 --> 00:15:15,159
You should go back as well.

280
00:15:16,960 --> 00:15:18,159
You're letting me go?

281
00:15:19,159 --> 00:15:20,039
Yes.

282
00:15:20,039 --> 00:15:22,639
(Release)

283
00:15:22,639 --> 00:15:24,000
How ridiculous.

284
00:15:24,879 --> 00:15:26,159
For two lifetimes,

285
00:15:27,000 --> 00:15:28,919
I did everything I could
to scheme against you.

286
00:15:29,480 --> 00:15:31,919
In the end, you're saving my life.

287
00:15:32,759 --> 00:15:33,879
Shen Zhinian,

288
00:15:35,000 --> 00:15:36,639
you're infuriating.

289
00:15:38,759 --> 00:15:40,279
My mother once told me

290
00:15:40,770 --> 00:15:42,799
that life is hard enough for women
in this world.

291
00:15:43,679 --> 00:15:45,120
We should help each other.

292
00:15:46,159 --> 00:15:47,279
Why make things difficult

293
00:15:48,399 --> 00:15:50,080
for one another?

294
00:15:55,320 --> 00:15:56,279
Go on.

295
00:16:10,960 --> 00:16:13,360
If there's another life,

296
00:16:14,200 --> 00:16:16,720
I won't fight anyone
for anything ever again.

297
00:16:40,159 --> 00:16:41,120
Take care.

298
00:16:43,000 --> 00:16:43,919
You too.

299
00:16:45,000 --> 00:16:46,720
I've been in this world
for fifteen years.

300
00:16:46,720 --> 00:16:48,390
This is my first time leaving
the capital.

301
00:16:48,960 --> 00:16:50,799
Now, I'm finally going to do
what I want.

302
00:16:52,279 --> 00:16:54,120
Are you really giving up

303
00:16:54,130 --> 00:16:55,620
the status
of the Liu family's eldest daughter?

304
00:16:56,080 --> 00:16:57,679
It's not some precious treasure.

305
00:16:58,090 --> 00:16:59,240
It was nothing but a shackle.

306
00:17:00,960 --> 00:17:02,840
Thank you for giving me
this fake identity.

307
00:17:03,320 --> 00:17:04,359
From now on,

308
00:17:04,480 --> 00:17:05,680
I'll use my real name again.

309
00:17:06,039 --> 00:17:07,839
You haven't told me your name.

310
00:17:08,079 --> 00:17:08,960
I'm not telling you.

311
00:17:09,079 --> 00:17:10,400
What if you come after me someday?

312
00:17:12,960 --> 00:17:14,839
Looks like you're smarter
than I thought.

313
00:17:15,640 --> 00:17:16,920
I'm leaving, Your Highness.

314
00:17:17,160 --> 00:17:18,400
The palace walls are tall.

315
00:17:18,559 --> 00:17:20,000
You can stay trapped there yourself.

316
00:17:20,000 --> 00:17:23,700
♪How many twists of fate
before we finally meet♪

317
00:17:24,100 --> 00:17:27,480
♪The melody drifts
across rivers and mountains♪

318
00:17:27,480 --> 00:17:28,680
My name is Tang Tingting.

319
00:17:28,839 --> 00:17:29,799
Shen Zhinian,

320
00:17:30,279 --> 00:17:31,039
see you.

321
00:17:42,440 --> 00:17:43,920
(Even if this world)

322
00:17:44,200 --> 00:17:46,200
(never leaves a path
for fragile branches,)

323
00:17:47,160 --> 00:17:49,000
(my heart holds unyielding strength.)

324
00:17:49,720 --> 00:17:52,279
(I'm determined to split stone apart
with these tender branches)

325
00:17:52,279 --> 00:17:54,160
(and climb to the highest place.)

326
00:17:56,720 --> 00:17:57,759
(Mother,)

327
00:17:58,119 --> 00:17:58,940
(I did it.)

328
00:18:25,000 --> 00:18:28,980
- Congratulations, Your Majesty amd Your Highness.
- Congratulations, Your Majesty amd Your Highness.

329
00:18:29,039 --> 00:18:31,000
- May you shine together
- May you shine together

330
00:18:31,000 --> 00:18:32,990
- and enjoy everlasting blessings!
- and enjoy everlasting blessings!

331
00:18:34,440 --> 00:18:35,480
Once upon a time,

332
00:18:35,559 --> 00:18:37,759
there was a wise and mighty emperor.

333
00:18:38,000 --> 00:18:41,319
With a sword and a horse,

334
00:18:41,680 --> 00:18:43,519
he conquered the whole realm.

335
00:18:43,690 --> 00:18:44,359
Isn't he amazing?

336
00:18:44,359 --> 00:18:45,039
He is!

337
00:18:47,359 --> 00:18:47,759
Oh.

338
00:18:47,800 --> 00:18:48,640
Your father is back.

339
00:18:48,799 --> 00:18:49,319
Go on.

340
00:18:49,440 --> 00:18:51,079
Father, you've returned from court.

341
00:18:51,920 --> 00:18:53,839
Go fetch my "armor".

342
00:18:54,079 --> 00:18:54,599
Mm.

343
00:18:55,300 --> 00:19:00,839
♪Dim lamps, concerns unheard by anyone♪

344
00:19:00,839 --> 00:19:03,039
What are you making for us tonight?

345
00:19:03,039 --> 00:19:05,680
A fragrant and delicious Peng fish soup.

346
00:19:07,200 --> 00:19:08,200
You're amazing.

347
00:19:08,240 --> 00:19:09,880
Father, you're amazing!

348
00:19:10,050 --> 00:19:11,599
What were you talking about just now?

349
00:19:11,839 --> 00:19:13,440
Mother was telling a story.

350
00:19:13,440 --> 00:19:14,839
Father, tell us one too.

351
00:19:14,839 --> 00:19:15,240
Alright.

352
00:19:15,250 --> 00:19:16,839
I'll tell you
the story of a tyrant emperor.

353
00:19:16,839 --> 00:19:18,240
That's not right.

354
00:19:18,240 --> 00:19:19,759
It's a wise and mighty

355
00:19:19,880 --> 00:19:21,319
emperor.

356
00:19:21,900 --> 00:19:23,710
(In the thirty-fourth year
of Hongye's reign,)

357
00:19:23,720 --> 00:19:24,880
(Emperor Xing passed away.)

358
00:19:25,119 --> 00:19:27,390
(Crown Prince Nangong Xuanyu
endured countless hardships.)

359
00:19:27,519 --> 00:19:29,480
(He executed six princes,)

360
00:19:29,759 --> 00:19:31,119
(purged the traitorous ministers,)

361
00:19:31,120 --> 00:19:32,200
(and ultimately ascended the throne.)

